 * Business rules:
 * - The configuration must be properly scoped: both channel_id and section_id must reference real entities.
 * - There must be no soft-deletion; on creation, deleted_at is null.
 *
 * This function ensures data integrity and proper scoping for configurations in the atomic configuration system.
 */
